# Claude Code / internal — ignore everything except shared skills.
# The self-healing skill is the canonical playbook for the auction pipeline
# and must propagate across worktrees / sessions, so it is tracked in git.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/

# Audit script persistent state (auto-generated)
scripts/audit/*.json

# Visual audit reports — committed by nightly workflow as the human-readable
# artifact (per the heal skill's Hard Rule 17). Replaces yesterday's, no
# accumulation. Ignoring would suppress them and break the heal loop.
# .gitkeep preserves the directory so first-run mkdir is a no-op.

# Internal docs (not production)
